OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1778519160
OL,3,C'Voice for the voiceless': How Agnes
OL,4,CLunny is transforming disability
OL,5,Csupport
OL,7,FOver 30 years ago, working in the
OL,8,Fcharity centre she saw the injustice
OL,9,Fof how those with disabilities were
OL,10,Ftreated. With little opportunity
OL,11,Foffered to them, many were
OL,12,Finstitutionalised, put into homes. Out
OL,13,Fof sight, out of mind. As she puts it
OL,14,Fdisabilities were seen first, the
OL,15,Fpeople behind those were seen after
OL,16,Fthat.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1778519160
OL,3,C'Voice for the voiceless': How Agnes
OL,4,CLunny is transforming disability
OL,5,Csupport
OL,7,FShe founded Positive Futures not just
OL,8,Fto provide help for those with
OL,9,Fdisabilities but to provide support
OL,10,Fwhich is person-centred. It designs
OL,11,Fsupport with the individual in mind.
OL,12,FShe's keen to emphasise it's not doing
OL,13,Ffor people, it's doing with people.
OL,14,FShe's emphatic that there is nobody
OL,15,Fthat cannot be supported to live a
OL,16,Fgood life, to have agency in their own
OL,17,Flifestyle.
OL,19,F'We're all individuals. We all have
OL,20,Fneeds. We all need to feel valued.'
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1778519160
OL,3,C'Voice for the voiceless': How Agnes
OL,4,CLunny is transforming disability
OL,5,Csupport
OL,7,FAgnes is adamant that by listening to
OL,8,Fpeople with disabilities and their
OL,9,Ffamilies, putting yourself in their
OL,10,Fshoes and developing empathy is key to
OL,11,Fproviding a real programme of support.
OL,12,FBy offering services which can work
OL,13,Ffor specific circumstances unlocks the
OL,14,Fpotential of the individual.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
