PN,44706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1778519160
OL,3,C'Voice for the voiceless': How Agnes
OL,4,CLunny is transforming disability
OL,5,Csupport
OL,7,FIronically, Agnes has been registered
OL,8,Fblind since she was 20. For her, it
OL,9,Fwas her parents who gave her the
OL,10,Ffearlessness to chase her dreams
OL,11,Fdespite her disability. She tells me
OL,12,Fthat she knows what it's like to be
OL,13,Fprejudiced against and it's this
OL,14,Fexperience which she says gives her
OL,15,Fthe fire in her belly.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
