FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1778519160
OL,3,C'Voice for the voiceless': How Agnes
OL,4,CLunny is transforming disability
OL,5,Csupport
OL,7,FAgnes says that she wants to be a
OL,8,F'voice for the voiceless.' She
OL,9,Fbelieves in being as close to those
OL,10,Fwith disabilities and their families
OL,11,Fas possible so she understands their
OL,12,Fissues, their challenges and uses her
OL,13,Finfluence to raise these needs with
OL,14,Fdecision makers.
OL,16,FWhen I ask about how she sees Positive
OL,17,FFutures evolving, I can sense Agnes's
OL,18,Fpride in what she has created.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
