PN,44708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1778519160
OL,3,C'Voice for the voiceless': How Agnes
OL,4,CLunny is transforming disability
OL,5,Csupport
OL,7,F'Positive Futures will always be part
OL,8,Fof me. It's like my first baby and you
OL,9,Fnever walk out on your children...I've
OL,10,Fseen so much happen that has really,
OL,11,Fliterally seen lives change. People
OL,12,Fhave described Positive Future as a
OL,13,Flife-line....our values are what shape
OL,14,Feverything we do. It's so important
OL,15,Fthat we keep people at the heart of
OL,16,Feverything we do...I see this
OL,17,Forganisation going from strength to
OL,18,Fstrength.'
OL,20,FSign up for our free weekly newsletter
OL,21,Fhere.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/9
